mb18_thumb.png" alt="favicon_32_thumb18" title="favicon_32_thumb18">&lt;/a> &lt;a href="http://www.majorleaguegaming.com/competitions/48">MLG Dallas – Summer Championship&lt;/a> . I had planned to finish out the sketch with a small/fun comic stripe to ‘illustrate’ (pun intended) the results. I hope next time we can see Grubby’s power unleashed! GG – Joshua ‘Raihn’ Keyes&lt;/p>
